  "texts": [
    "The organoids were fixed in 4% PFA for 20 min to 1 hour at 4 °C and emerged in 30% sucrose (w/v) overnight at 4 °C to dehydrate the tissue.",
    "The next day, the organoids were embedded in Gelatin/ Sucrose solution and froze on dry ice.",
    "Gelatin/Sucrose solution was prepared by dissolving 7.5% gelatin (w/v) in 10% sucrose (w/v) at 37 °C.",
    "The embedded samples were stored in sealed plastic bags in a -80 °C freezer.",
    "Sections were collected and dried for one hour at RT before storing at -80 °C."
  ],
